						</Viewbox>
						<PathIcon Margin="0 8 0 0" Data="M896 576c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32v137.8c0 22.9-9 44.5-25.3 60.8s-38 25.4-60.9 25.4H246.2c-22.9 0-44.5-9-60.8-25.3-16.4-16.4-25.4-38-25.4-60.9V608c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32v137.8C96 828.6 163.4 896 246.2 896h531.7c82.8 0 150.2-67.4 150.2-150.2V608c-0.1-17.7-14.4-32-32.1-32z"/>
